ğŸ”¹ Mansabdari System (Very Important)

Introduced by Akbar

Features:

Every officer given a rank (Mansab)

Two numbers:

Zat â†’ personal rank

Sawar â†’ number of cavalry maintained

Transferable posts

Salary paid in cash or jagir

